        <h3>Compatibility with Browsers and Assistive Technology</h3>
        <p>
            This website is designed to be compatible with the following assistive technologies and browsers:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Recent versions of popular screen readers including JAWS, NVDA, and VoiceOver</li>
            <li>Recent versions of major browsers including Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge</li>
            <li>Speech recognition software</li>
            <li>Screen magnification software</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            This website is not compatible with browsers older than 3 major versions or with Internet Explorer.
        </p>

        <h3>Formal Complaints</h3>
